The React and ReactDom are two packages in the React Ecosystem
The react package is the core part of the React Ecosystem. 
It can be used to create components that can be used together to build complex UIs. 
React can be used to define the UIs and program the behaviour of the UI due to the change in the 
applications change . And can render the components to the dom .

React Dom is also a package that provide methods to render the components to the dom .
Actually it provides integration between the dom and the React.
It acts as a glue between the React and React Dom
